lank"&gt;发誓要“坚定地做出回应”&lt;/a&gt; 。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;特朗普现有的目标&lt;/strong&gt;也正在准备他们的防御能力。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=719fc837c6d94a21bceb0ef6f8d38dcb&amp;amp;_e=2qAE5aiE8xD9hGjdNt4-UQxvyOsBpl56mYs881smlsZ_yU4tJfav5ZrgbLsmbwGZjWe8k713ievGJJ8k9ioZM5dcEcULn15W9TRIdrPplQZy2Elbx9W4jwVEoCTyaKUV8L9Te0btEpuWeXW1BbWvOFmtRklFcOFN4UGMxKFBVekYtYgCzEf45lv8t2-Xe6mnZ32nCPI4nSf-VRiKLBlIblLLY412tNx8TTg0N5tkmAy8ZXwxNsy5CmF7MnWXlPHc9fmkxyRNyK3QeIGz6I9jSMtdaHpbSz7SsKjXVojPtccXfdNuMqxDuzGM0zHH3AdlMw2EgnY_hZKzloQRJ-k_nA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;加拿大采取了危机反应&lt;/a&gt;，与共同的大流行相似，而墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·辛巴姆（Claudia Sheinbaum）表示，她将&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=719fc837c6d94a21bceb0ef6f8d38dcb&amp;amp;_e=2qAE5aiE8xD9hGjdNt4-UalGzShh_I-Z9O3fAnLOMJJueGLgUfT68PF69wltgHEviRZSU2t8YiEb-MClxEU00YbjHSpXraoNhPJe21wAeuxtMt9JXXfofFlYNARf3teY2qsQtbHABXeu1iwFwOdGQewwwbQNA1IUFKDl_K3nICih0rYuz_tnPhvD1Asj08vTHH9p9WuPbTx4nlrD0lr32Cy04g4XtqhfZhXdGjY5gLXwg145VecPSxviV_K-RibFLPqVNhKcc3MCZsKy5qoZfyccSweYDxw3MVUXhPAbyWUdeEfcB1jVlQ4MroVBJB735zqYRugksh1Gbr4Q1D7rww%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;提出一个“计划B”&lt;/a&gt;来保护该国。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=719fc837c6d94a21bceb0ef6f8d38dcb&amp;amp;_e=2qAE5aiE8xD9hGjdNt4-UcGzpQDXHf7A8YnQN8c3SukEsd30E12F9ohBjUjpf4RMz9-vUBj3gDZlSi0mDs_WpxXuSCa54B3AHrXgKI2IjkylPIUI_iNjedZXmrSi8hXqZBVpCIH85g2z61oOaSiX-fA5Ihm8m8N7JLNZSI9IDMw1OTFbz3NZskA48kkN1H6iigaSw-Fe_yqKu1Vc1FDdx41oiF1ta9g-o0YvSvMIjD1Ni-0PtInGKzvP4b7IDu0qyOsyaRKd9h0yYwXGkiBreNByRIOq8sQRtGLAID2EeUc25dmaIzmer8OkTEDRTXGfLG6osoo4SlI-21Bl6MA1bw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;中国的反应更加柔和&lt;/a&gt;，不详细说明“相应的对策”。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=719fc837c6d94