XY-5g4BhivTzuqR0AttKQpJY92nOqQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;本周&lt;/a&gt;将通过降低其&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=3f3eebaf66454d5faa57fe13e8df9f64&amp;amp;_e=9wu-416qr2fd1NFCYVXP3QCEz67GDhSBPl628L84PwKxOVApEOAM7KLPTXub70jnoyU4Mfb622NyjgYQ4fUd1e7lea2wLfc54wnHVtWc-prBCbuLenTKlcwGowKFNGiHW2KVq_YTFwFv1y3_95rHC6Y7RIx5pW1_7T4jSxB-Hx65OkbdkGXwhewrE8DrELeZL0FMRr53fLpfrkCoU_ZikIuuSOjpss319kcJJCv3gjmSpMIYlvv6U8a_xU9yZuTZiHqjYBocdY_VGHGPJ0Svu8Pv4qZYY1okrVhzJCCMN_fI_SpRULxceu11PE2v4ZUCCxDp73exVNZvzr6UBXRmcg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;增长前景&lt;/a&gt;，并警告她的十月预算将推动通货膨胀率提高通货膨胀，从而对英国大臣进行打击。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;莫斯科财产与伦敦竞争，因为富裕的俄罗斯人&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=3f3eebaf66454d5faa57fe13e8df9f64&amp;amp;_e=9wu-416qr2fd1NFCYVXP3QVFYFZHikgyJ7myNwv1zD8TnbUxdyopqJdhUWHOuCmDcSRtZNB8b6K6MZtMtiUIYaecQjDljntq3wZqactI6notfeaVmR6dS49op4a7lQiW05VffuArB_9XaeaUrx59q3eMPaY8Ws-uVG7LZEz5cC-57uEQAwVi7FMSwrGiUtsTKmXpLfbqU8yFr_JuztpQZFFi7yTA7s33_42FsHxVy2D3l6lIlbN9yQZ4lmVTMWN2SLAF0fnkd3GvEpR76bKaxQ_YY1fwsWIesWtBsJFASaFZtyC2AyQ-3PTSBZlvkASPoQDBTRH-CKnbsgo7-rdC4w%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;将现金带回家&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;印度的总理在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=3f3eebaf66454d5faa57fe13e8df9f64&amp;amp;_e=9wu-416qr2fd1NFCYVXP3V1HAw-Dyj0zyGE-q8fvo6R3CyoQWskt9CeG3E4q5_WUMNSjUJ3iCQZkTwrhNF3q993iPKc1eXPxu0ytARqwRvl1ekyo59Mce690tuTSeu2BUy3vdKwqYbHVoP9LBfVR66gXN-tTUHdo3q6TDZTSc5ONeVBLxeMshnCxzbABhUI_j7F-T02iWi0TOVX6ZH2nJpTZp69oihLMOIJBKs2Z5kHm7JBvc9pVKwmosUFuVPB9hK46vYn4yu3L-hCMymX0Cp03KgGp-OR8Cf7PqORujf5GgDZA35V1JD04n-Fa1P_e0namhlmFT16XUNHMvUeYTA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;预算&lt;/a&gt;中给&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=3f3eebaf66454d5faa57fe13e8df9f64&amp;amp;_e=9wu-416qr2fd1NFCYVXP3WyzsZRUZtjupJh4J2Qt4cm3-Dn9CLdVQR9601uXYDiaPNqFsxLd9_-HSa7TBHjJ2VVfBKxKV8dLGyvl9_qBs6m-_z6jMDbExsG9uS1jnFPS7X4IkOjtHOUGWNTATsE1hz0ThbC9elK9uPhmrIUfdrThzprqc6fWOTEawNBjyeoHJMGTqJFRw2LzoA2hIjpUd1V9McJl89ZJeL_aQlSWxxhGTRld-o7eKX1jsNFdWt-43XFuTe2AanhI-7mcvU1d6Abw3S047TF5mwCmAH_Qw2dOfdbr-aKTBnYzUVEN8o2MSRwD-hEMafZSbgmAlE1_Yw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;中产阶级&lt;/a&gt;提供了明显的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=3f3eebaf66454d5faa57fe13e8df9f64&amp;amp;_e=9wu-416qr2fd1NFCYVXP3f5kVrbtdrrN7e7dQFFj5jYtRbKAVfvXcIjkrn1_WYch9OLV8Bs3ZUQ6KSrNkarlqDh101E5ej5K8I0rJWTKEmWYrFuInAxVJZ1hMZv4ZLqq5NAbobmlUpBCuV73WOh7X7YmbwCtOituLXhCExksMGu4EwIZezZJNVh5s2ZKbDzC9GaBtIHaYQa0xQnLoPPi9F9o680A4nS4vxjVRuspvlHrUWthvo-6HZ_-JavICiqfFxX9IUuZBAVA5H_NVe8d0wc3OYv7NvX_-2gYR5wapjnQwxE5grEsIBgC2pix05hBxUNLwffdy6C5FlyJZJ_3uQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;税收减免&lt;/a&gt;，但&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=3f3eebaf66454d5faa57fe13e8df9f64&amp;amp;_e=9wu-416qr2fd1NFCYVXP3YP36lMIPyLvkywqLcjMipCJPZMOFIsZ-Fgf9MT8dm1Ycz3aMmUYjc8LzGTEgeIukqRBdMsMfiDj1pnTrinspY4--qI6mTkj9KhNyOrrD2AKAAMqUplNLyTES9nmgfsuSkF-rJTIJ00AWIyNCXUcJwG0NPDZ5_8-_JWI15zbzWSnoYzHOWbOXaAEPRLALE53dXvEjUc_M_ZGzzj44yW5SoL7yj6f9ckLTOJPqI5rZhYWv8PoVL_Hhz9h6vKvn8B_BejOqwiUpc053bJOCdu83ALso_dAGbb8A_2-MMZinmUosDi8L-KmCikaP8j_4Ek0iw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;几乎没有给投票反对他的失业者提供的支持&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·辛巴姆（Claudia Sheinbaum）提名何塞·加布里埃尔·库德拉·加西亚（Jose Gabriel Cuadra Garcia）加入&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=3f3eebaf66454d5faa57fe13e8df9f64&amp;amp;_e=9wu-416qr2fd1NFCYVXP3a469manC5heUUpgghaKiiqR0F60HqeR0DGwPKeJKWXwTSvBgOYUmievM301a0mAOtJ_lZte5cAC54EYXv46kL6Sc3rR4Zi1d4WUYWvH3TF8jdxH46ZcKo7U5G1Nv7xqvWLOXGjaofZSdXtqVbTzclnBk6tf4VqB-k9TG1DIr3Wn3RiKCKi6Xsm3UHOLWHpohKQuIXkrilIWknygmaFdp0LeTTI5vhqDVAg3hp3CvsDlDvINIhlFRCXWW8UJlz-DKqRZZq7pe6Qj3TtzMPFUoAj9oGV83BKveSnZ5ZEz8Su3RzWZJOqTmrAcCdvT9RyEkw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;中央银行&lt;/a&gt;的五人董事会。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;土耳其&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=3f3eebaf66454d5faa57fe13e8df9f64&amp;amp;_e=9wu-416qr2fd1NFCYVXP3fCO1tKQE6PaeJh8WnDOtvyCQWpczzo5uLjJpx1DZwWeMkn1-FgbPBfnAJeh3CoGCkG3-aAP_fXLmcltDKTgce2KC2yq_Dmbo3CnvSPR6YTyzBswXRsBjac2GRs30odx2Ktw8ubbIjcOB27MCmaSTlKu6tx5TRQsjbUlQGfiJrkyYYFUKx4atwrb8eGJpZTWw3O4f-lcjIEmqNKtdfc89T9QZLq7126pQRhPphqkxn5p6rHLXMvKay-8igxBHXbpevNKEZ0Q1w8P007QOD4HzPg55ASXUJTVs-vLm_Eqjws0KOpobRQIGQlP9u2plk6SKg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;通货膨胀&lt;/a&gt;率少于预期。同时，政府&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=3f3eebaf66454d5faa57fe13e8df9f64&amp;amp;_e=9wu-416qr2fd1NFCYVXP3XBLjcFWYB5Dqz4Z3utyH3FkwiCWNkqXv2Z0XcIDkEApFA0QTyvCR4vEvxtC80Qefn6QNCP8lD5Z-2aCxeoBe1Hr2DgF5pr76nVSqoYZKQ0R5lWCd97EGLdG-aA19v-LdLCQrfMgVHzipIkNcLEHWg8w0P9WF2vaTKIwy_Rjfioh3mgR27YXUzSe4ctqgX_i30YeJSbMcUsU0gG99m-OxVVok_9bNm_UEcr0IWO0yHk259KCg_jUtZr19Yv1ScJQT-efox95Dfsx5e9GsVYqHbg-qaG4Kp-fvHjaBOMgC33b8gOSp8Dmr2rtTvQCLdOjxw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;对存款和资金提出了预扣税&lt;/a&gt;，以支持其预算。 &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;未来的一周&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;美国劳动力市场可能以又一个月的稳定增长开始了2025年，而备受期待的年度修订可能会在过去几年中显示出更为温和的招聘速度。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;根据彭博社调查的经济学家的中位数预测，在劳动力市场从飓风的影响和重大罢工中恢复过来的情况下，薪资在1月的进步之后提高了170,000。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;周五的每月工作报告还将包括劳工统计局的年度修订。该机构将使从去年3月的工资核算水平与从失业保险计划中得出的季度调查进行更全面的工作计数。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/in41ihtS6FNA/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/in41ihtS6FNA/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;在其他地方，可能是从英国到印度再到墨西哥的税率，欧元区的通货膨胀数据将是其中之一。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=3f3eebaf66454d5faa57fe13e8df9f64&amp;amp;_e=9wu-416qr2fd1NFCYVXP3TGGZos-2cJ_40H1L4aaMPalPp3PT9muikTkE3Tlidfj5d0CDf43bSefoRgUe9fAF1DD8hoGI8xReZHv9J8D01FUa03mD4uZe4FMya9jwjXPeyDLRVi47wE8RPDxRVi1hvKa4DpbL5DaQl92JlDpyBjAY-hY-Zc1RxS_PzoUe3HeTwl7sAu3dAn0-KY847o7b_sDUapEUVIjLiWTxHWXC3ZwlxoPOcxzproh148j2bFzF69tSleLuNjjGErcjy3mrKlgTrCjIgb5fo9EHLtGdMh13pnVLSnpu2XfafxuEu1vNUVTxix7u1NuvcOgvWQjIQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;请参阅此处&lt;/a&gt;的剩余经济活动。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;需要知识研究&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=3f3eebaf66454d5faa57fe13e8df9f64&amp;amp;_e=9wu-416qr2fd1NFCYVXP3S5kipfUvYoC5S-TGBBMcZRiD-HC3wjTcQQIQYbGWLs2pP3wa1Kh1s84--Su4WHL8c_1yVk8MpTMeoMgQXFMdsNRabCsTUTlyhNHNT_lGI2XrGr96wfSDGI_UwppEBDHMnfmAK7KmjhoPX6Sr81eKXQhr-dLf7zv10TzPqGlOmlDIqRVqWobT2jh88pSuDg3reQxhepzKxXlldsA162oz31Qq1lCKPcLiToymGOvdqldqUbm8RivKlr-G9xuQjBcqyZc_dNEHxGwX8P3k8jyq__cDkLoL6W2f-o54RPnz7vfmmLAcxuXN1JvkqXxX4vjZQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;新研究表明&lt;/a&gt;，妇女对英格兰银行的信任比男性要比男性少，而且对生活成本的冲击感到更加挤压，这强调了中央银行在提高公众声誉面临的挑战。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;根据这项研究，牛津大学在牛津大学进行的研究使用了对家庭对通货膨胀的季度&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=3f3eebaf66454d5faa57fe13e8df9f64&amp;amp;_e=9wu-416qr2fd1NFCYVXP3bhv8Sy8FzidVYMLoF-6oZYWaJzG5HLrmnubiYSbV9xE8Nesf2FAAIQGCLE8ko0rQMtbCLLT_--jIOFhT4nbAH_7NNoM96j9VbkRZ4N32P2DMdkDWZ_U4UoO4urUJrZwg0mTdjQGMnCLzuC7FD5lV6eTKogGVBBbq41PG_-Z4fjFSGt8Mih3G5yMc6gQRspMJQtHK3Iq6JXqiR3v64cfrSuRrnBQf8yg9xM8oJSyTDXBWXDYoNUNVbdi15SE2fmvbtA13Pikfl7g9QaZQd9R7YHRR6mQ_anNwmbaTM0so8UbyvEYPfmHgnjb4XiGgwBN2KRns8Q75-h58CYVJ0rd8l2NkoErlG_oCl8d2AUqI_VDK5rEOq-rHWYwathyB3bNeje1Sr-pSvOQZjdES2K2QRo4nlaRpQvmP5xoY-2BK-gF_y3Af7bztwM5aAdf6cZsxG61dUrckbfrpI6zRnp1AFw%3D" target="_blank" title="关联"&gt;调查&lt;/a&gt;的数据，对BOE的表现感到满意。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3GWfbdm7CMQ/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3GWfbdm7CMQ/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;根据分析，妇女对BOE有更负面看法的部分原因在于她们对通货膨胀的反应方式，该分析控制了年龄和收入等因素。当面对价格上涨时，妇女通过节省更多和购物以寻找折扣来收紧预算。另一方面，男人只需要求更高的薪水即可。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;合着者迈克尔·麦克马洪（Michael McMahon）和洛维萨·赖希（Lovisa Reiche）写道：“妇女感到更加经济上的压力，而男性可能会因通货膨胀而主动避免经济损失。” &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;来自彭博社的更多信息&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;每天享受经济学吗？&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;阅读更多&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=3f3eebaf66454d5faa57fe13e8df9f64&amp;amp;_e=9wu-416qr2fd1NFCYVXP3R3XwavYIXZb9qAuPpvQkeuovQEg0T1K6J00ZvCRo7bBxXhaxRl1AB-p7g_R7TsFTOie8sqxFOiYw9j5qQDbXOWTZ4Plit3ZsMOxrwnu-p1Ry3JgB6AXXMWyR4qFeB53OJh5E-xOwiVR05QWxPuadN8VPs3btEeFKpwDlxMBP2vsDYB7kVYp8AWr6MgHErARE6pLjX7o2v_jN823XuLvKhfNIFyrj7ryQivFiql8E65Gg18ArdLlwzLlbGVn7Pdm2xunw_JfyCQqfmfaKnsgCfugCyecQGaSj5KA4v72jYf1kLCtDtTMXEcktIoMeQhxiQ%3D%3D" title="彭博网站"&gt;经济故事&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;关注我们&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=3f3eebaf66454d5faa57fe13e8df9f64&amp;amp;_e=9wu-416qr2fd1NFCYVXP3ZpTZQqUZTCrP77IJCK0DJzZchUr20Uu5DjXasEdm8xQgzaIAfC9jWeVetce8trHEa2qEv_Bj9DJALB1mnQ5YKFhmRnwK8z7LqBCbEGmcliPe5o_fc_r02GK-O8xcAdQ5oV32PDrB2OD4pTAGo4oObv2T_-5dRb-lzqdxB2h5cqaD10GFlA_7nvgyjdXc_Oj-A26ZvDH2BYgF0Yno7AIFnnksT83Zmv4X0hKEIWc7Zsfl8ChnMeX-Y0hCI50sVg_zow3bOxl9uGjnFfu1rMK6-EHdpSrxv-xTjtvKmyI2MHxM-Ky85AK6v0QZJKCd_k_fJBWqj7j9bPRFny1euPlw24%3D"&gt;@CONOMANS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sa