rget="_blank"&gt;对关税的征收&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;提出了柔和的反应&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;，商务部在一份声明中&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=423ab8e4d7b54b35a53d8256a31c2841&amp;amp;_e=eSdKDd30V7d0mthiYL_TNeiO84A6ozjoDtc4428w-Skce9SulYNbX4beXRF6qSDts_swTjwlTbBTjeEEiDfJWWpAZdBpwbgdQQVajxNrnGU5oUC2-lznyD3IyFkvkQ4NtU9m5U1mH4oAG65eZGLkSEI-4zs6CVd0cjfGwRU_TVmnmBfSohXDx4BMQk4n62wn7fwZDp1AEz8KDw1uMgWrBmtMxfKHe8iVA95Idc6vWNJmNE1Fpnx9VqGWzSugsJ7ROICIDzEP_wdhrti-cwmHH87Wc4eAEpJBImKr55s6Fp5ohu_pzb5k1hSZzj2iK3okhKWCuYFbBsB2k0n1Sav8lw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;表达了强烈的&lt;/a&gt;“不满”，并誓言“相应的对策”而没有详细说明。欧洲联盟表示，如果美国在集团上&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=423ab8e4d7b54b35a53d8256a31c2841&amp;amp;_e=eSdKDd30V7d0mthiYL_TNYjJSbJPK3r2u9n7nAKr6pbjn2wjywDjZsFyQcTL6nsgKBjQzrY_73VC6KHJ6186P2VlfSOPNpkcSoZQjoWn1CuSvgFYlBrS1WIoCJCxwHtfqGqzdRjlkDNIL6yH4_KDo3C8FJqkETJNt2A8dutLSZJdOElIG1NoQ6_cuOaY3pHUlmjYvQVMRz9LP1f3PTt_OhTOwpQ1ul1odxHUoWf8AIrY-pLeI7Zase0tfr5Xv5g97btJAPD4Fl7zTUFJCYtDYuKBIg2j2S0bJUN0mxkelSbbhooHQRnqeKMfgc3VDvZ3nICDoMcXvTpvPCblQGxADQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;征收关税&lt;/a&gt;，并且会员国明天将在华沙举行的部长会议上讨论这种可能性。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;欧洲政府受到马斯克的政治攻击的政府&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;正在比较巴西的笔记，这迫使他去年在其X平台上遵守对仇恨言论和虚假新闻的要求。巴西正在与社会媒体网络进行&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=423ab8e4d7b54b35a53d8256a31c2841&amp;amp;_e=eSdKDd30V7d0mthiYL_TNQVqgXJ8pkJkvMrPkdztLmIWQJ7I6FSqrTjm048t1v_8zeYyL8SUBSJIUSknAHzsOTsneaRH1v8MPESvq6WeHLwFZiFs38DsVQkImO0J-xrYQW9SBNsvIOjAdjWtU4zqevTgOBbm_7FXs3-gzo5VhnBRkOWvA_1w12wtWwxOR_wzGnwzA60a4yTwS5e1qnsQu