ick?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=125bab7c3de54f0caf256f5bc084533a&amp;amp;_e=pJ5UF5_r1btWivWgV99_dGW_1tXz9GAEoPr8qB7FFISuXtjW8dZO7DmyFoHATe90Rp7ooNFLz-cyxBxt2iHbKp82s7deOwCWXE4Pijg1pbw5194cJ8h_frRGTzWfFJRAu7Fb4_rHqOdoV5ukmZS2Oic-nShDbMqgO13cJu4aPHJeRDQSybiLtbHXaWQpjXbEtMt0i0wzYqShkWhuJOMCXKtmUPWiAjoETMqhkVWh8WqSy3KIU0N8Ksm_xBLt34QZjYpdvrY-yzaN7KopU8oRj9KsAiPKWMUQsYa2pjfPw5qytUnhgkqWcYIDPHNX44bm0AKb3SPhNW1eGGPeoaZfr9inim7-Pkxw-CA_6F4YPGfGS8f9zrW9D7agnT-z4wQnPtgue6lfBURsrUY-KM3HnOKQVCm8mDK1GUjkCvMHvZT4hy9ebBQ86z-0L8VLK7wR5YtlcQDrkQLT9VtIt8tG6I2Vp8s7hSawRhoxYFP2L5erMJFoHhrHUO3Kgp58Ow1qRESdd_TatRGw-BblDVeC_w%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;在这里取得联系&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 20px 0px;"&gt;&lt;table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding-bottom: 10px;"&gt;您收到了此消息，因为您已订阅彭博的《预报新闻通讯》。如果朋友转发了此消息， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=125bab7c3de54f0caf256f5bc084533a&amp;amp;_e=pJ5UF5_r1btWivWgV99_dGzrAsXPDz71n5nAwGZ0ZsDtadgpdBrqXKkXd7BWCTspCGBNiaM5JOwzB_64Uc-TLplNPH2PGJ7qpI5YZemII7L5KD76Q7P5QR1s_0NFYgknPi7hudgOnNw9gG5stfsPFvkWyore0ft6LdEFffBU5L1E-5vxOZT90M1rS-NiWOIw1xk_y7ImtqRqc3r1oZZ0D--PDoRokfgRAM6cnbZ8AKVzGPwtCHn78TwOuywNQjqtgGB_2edA0lo78E960NBzrY7huiaJoor9jvglh62E4BF7KAOMxrLHvIVAj_RqszdwPwEbqSBj1oshV2NvhtTbaA%3D%3D"&gt;请在此处注册&lt;/a&gt;以将其放入收件箱中。 &lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 150%;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: c